overview:
MovieWeb is a social entertainment platform that connects film fans to the films that matter to them, across the web, connected televisions and mobile devices.

MovieWeb drives discovery, engagement & sharing while empowering conversation among fans, making it easy and fun to find, follow, see and discuss with friends and other fans and never miss the movies you want to see.

MovieWeb helps users find, follow and see the films they don’t want to miss, in theaters, on disc, streaming, or when they’re out on television or available online. Users can keep track of what they’ve seen and share ratings and reviews, collections and more.
